Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我連累你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego和恐怖分子的Rideback 都是岡倉先生製作的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那傢伙告訴了你些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是個連自己都能欺騙的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我認為他說的是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego不過是我對過去的留戀罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻把你牽扯了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:40.69,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:40.69,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:42.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:42.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:49.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:49.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:56.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:56.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:02:00.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:02:00.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:03.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:03.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:06.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:06.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:27.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:27.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:31.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:31.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:33.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:33.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:36.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:36.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
